name: Between Worlds
description: @merzmensch presents. #MERZistance. I worked for years in a big University. It was indeed a small society, with its ups and downs, its crisis, its insanity and geniality. Life-changing experience. But always, even being in dispair or confusion (and it's not easy to bring me into this mode), I've looked up and saw it: the sky. And I knew there is way more out there than this "human-zoo" called reality.
